  "detailed_description": "Shoot lasers in space because a fish told you to. Ernesto's Asteroid Arcade is a twin-stick side-scrolling space shoot-em-up which tells the story of a man side-scrolling in space and shooting-em-up with twin-sticks. This game has at least 2 characters in it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329390/extras/3475ef3dc2ae163b10a14b80693d7b87.avif?t=1768357703\" width=480 height=160 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A story campaign with at least 6 Different Levels (there's 11)<br></li><li> An Endless mode for replayability with 6 different ships to unlock<br></li><li> A story told with branching dialogue paths<br></li><li> Full controller support, cloud saves, and achievements</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329390/extras/53d27b5169e9a2182372368409a48780.apng?t=1768357703\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329390/extras/53d27b5169e9a2182372368409a48780.poster.avif?t=1768357703\" class=\"bb_img\" width=480 height=160 /></picture></span>",
